args:
Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: When I am President of the United States...on Day One, I will tell Pennsylvania energy workers to FRACK, FRACK, FRACK, and DRILL, DRILL, DRILL! We will have Energy INDEPENDENCE and Energy DOMINANCE, as we did just 4 short years ago—But if Kamala is reelected, your costs will go UP and your lights will go OUT…
